data.description: Excellent opportunity for investors, vacationers or first time home buyers! This home offers ceiling fans, window coverings, laminate/ tile floors and newer appliances. Near the river, boat launches & Rotary Park. Has RV and Boat parking with ( 15'W, 37'L & 12' H) covered double carport. A fully fenced secure property plus additional 18' long parking in front behind the gate. Additional storage in shed as well. Plenty of reasons to call this beautiful house your home. Financeable!!
